Otherwise, we say nothing and celebrate in the incredibly beautiful highland landscape of Scotland that was the backdrop to the Viking world about a thousand years ago.
It would be ideal if more mature filmmakers had an interest in existentialism and excellent travelling.
When a film is aimed at several target groups, it is a pity that they are mutually exclusive.
Director Winding Refn has been considered, since the release of Pusher, his trilogy about the ferocious and stylish drug dealer, as a kind of Danish Quentin Tarantino, but he refuses to bring a little more humor to the mainstream or introduce a little less brutality to art and experimental cinema.
Most art film enthusiasts must be horrified by the brain that spreads around and into the intestines.
Action film buffs are bored to death when the Borgne embarks, for reasons that can be freely interpreted, with a group of violent Christian missionaries on a ship bound for Jerusalem; they are drowned for an eternity in the stillness and fog before the crew arrives in America and continues to be silent.
