The disclosure of the US embassy note, which was only made public late last night, Moscow time, will surely stir up discontent within the Russian government; and while Luzhkov may be blamed, to some extent, for Moscow's failures, it could be an opportunity for the Kremlin to show that it is resolving the problem.
