The Red Bull team now employs 180 highly qualified young professionals who, equipped with powerful computer equipment, analyse and design all kinds of modifications to the cars.
The Siemens executive explained that the PLM software is capable of analysing and improving all the elements of Red Bull cars except the engine, which is the exclusive responsibility of Renault.
